body_html:
Can you please try installing the nightly build of TensorFlow (pip install tf-nightly) and see if this is still a problem?

It looks like b927df5 upgrades TensorFlow on Windows to a newer version of protobuf, and that patch wasn't present in the 1.4 release.

body:
Can you please try installing the nightly build of TensorFlow (`pip install tf-nightly`) and see if this is still a problem? 

It looks like b927df57f0c09ea62a855795e340d6daf70553df upgrades TensorFlow on Windows to a newer version of protobuf, and that patch wasn't present in the 1.4 release.
